detaileddescription.para: CAUTION: While adding the new error code The comment section for that error code is must, else that error message will not be handle by web. String within the comment section in the same line of error code enum will be displayed as error message on the web. Format of the comment section should follow doxygen format comment as below. Macro to define success status
File not found, Cannot perform the operation
File write failed, Cannot perform the operation
File truncate failed, Cannot perform the operation
Update failed it can be anything like (tree update, servd internal update, csd internal update, etc)
Add operation failed, max limit reached
Delete operation failed, system expects this entry
Validataion Failed, Cannot perform the operation
Add Operation Failed, due to non-instancable property of the object
Value is not number or less than expected value
Value is not number or greater than expected value
String length is less than expected length
String length is greater than expected length
Read only parameter, Cannot perform the operation
String not found or String match failed
ubus timeout happend on get/set request
SL failed to complete the operation or timed out

briefdescription.para: Enum containing the type of error code which can be returned from the framework modules like servd, csd, and cal. Buffer error code -200 to -240.
